column8: Spirits, let us educate this whelp!
Spirits, I have one ripe for the plucking for you!
Gods of the Spirit Realm, help me show him his true potential!
I will use the power of the Spirits!
By the power of the Spirit Realm!!
Lord Volibear, I call upon your might!
Lord Volibear, give me your strength!
Darius! I have a delicious war down here for you!
Teemo I have a job for you!
A wayward soul for you to guide, Lady Ahri!
I shall scour you from this place.
A solid hit. There may be hope for you yet!
It shall take more than that!
The Spirits are on my side!
Come, show us what you're made of!
Alistar and I will never be defeated.
Hm, Alistar you are worthy indeed.
None can escape the grasp of our obsession, Alistar.
Back to the hell that spawned you.
Run back crying to daddy, you whelp.
You had no chance against the Champion.
When next we meet, it shall go even worse.
Elysium is for the great, not for the likes of you!
Your foolish attempts shall get you nowhere!
I'll never tire of collecting your soul.
You are forever doomed to fail.
That was for last time, whelp!
Thus I reassert my status as the Champion!
If you beat the bull, you may have what it takes...
I'll get you back for that!
Now you have my whole attention!
Feel the force of my obsession!
Whelp! Who taught you such sloppy technique?!
Whelp! You are unfit to walk these hallowed passageways!
You are little more than a snivelling pup.
How your soul must be quivering inside!
You have a lot of nerve!
Come, runt! Attack with everything you have!
A mongrel like you stains the perfection of Elysium!
What's the matter, little runt? Afraid I shall beat you again?
Any last words, runt? Before I slay you once again?
If you ever manage to procure a chariot, I will happily beat you in a race too.
Haha, filth. No better than the dirt underneath my shoes.
No wonder your mother didn't want you.
My interest in you wanes with each of your failures.
Undeserving whelp, have you ever had to earn anything yourself?
Feeling lost? Don't worry, I shall be more than happy to save your wayward soul.
Stand there while I run you through, yet again.
Attack me, if you must. Either way, I shall crush you.
Unwelcome pustule! I shall run you through!
Nrrh I'll make you pay for this!!
No! What depths you stoop to, whelp!!
How dare you, you little bastard!
I shall get you for this!!
No!! I'd just completed the repairs!
Again you did this to me?!
My chariot may be gone, but we shall rise again!
What is the meaning of this?
What is the Spirit of Night doing here?
Why is Death on his side?!
I'm not afraid of the Night!
You beat me once already, Aphelios!
We can take more than that!
Lord Volibear, what have I done?!
Lady Nami I thought I was your favourite?!
Lady Nami, is this all because...?!
Soraka you are supposed to protect ME!
Darius, I thought you recognized true power!
Now is not the time for one of your pranks, Teemo!
Does this mean I'm not invited to the party, Teemo?
You destroy my chariot, I destroy you, end of tale.
Chariots can be repaired, rebuilt! Honor cannot.
That was for my beautiful chariot, useless runt!
Your foul deeds shall go unsung, mark you my words.
There. I shall await when next you clamber to these heights.
If only you could hear the roaring crowd.
Such a spectacle is it not?
Nothing like battling before an audience!
Spirits, I require your assistance, now!
Lissandra, something for you to freeze!
I thought we were friends, Liss?!
But Lissandra, what did I do?!
Spirits, I require your assistance, now!
I swear I'll get you yet!
They know our victory is certain here!
That cheering's not for you, whelp!
We shall prevail for you in the stands!
Are you enjoying yourselves in the stands?!
Such fervor coming from this crowd!
To all who came to see us fight, thank you!
We owe everything to our audience!
Keep cheering, as we battle to the last!
The roaring of the crowd fills me with strength!
You shall have what you came to see!
To all our fans, we dedicate this fight to you!
Your slouching form is but a laughingstock compared to my superior technique!
I'll show you how it's done, runt!
You are all talk, you know that, don't you, filth?!
Cower all you wish! I shall pierce your heart anyway!
Come fight me in the open, whelp, or are you scared?!
Ha! He thinks that he can beat us!
Stand and fight like a man, you coward!
Offering your soul for my collection?
I shall enjoy crushing you with my chariot, runt!
I'll run you down like a dog!
Show me your back and I shall stab you right through it, whelp!
He makes a mockery of us!
Guh, I shall not lose to you again!
Khh, I am not finished yet!
